ate court times allocated for vaccinated and unvaccinated players?  (ie &#8211; specific time slots throughout the week for either the entire club or specific courts)</label><div class='ginput_container ginput_container_likert'><table aria-label='As a temporary measure during times of outbreak, to what extent would you support the idea of having separate court times allocated for vaccinated and unvaccinated players?  (ie - specific time slots throughout the week for either the entire club or specific courts)' class='gsurvey-likert' id='input_89_4'><thead><tr><th id='likert_col_1_89_4' scope='col' role='presentation' class='gsurvey-likert-choice-label'>Great idea &#8211; let&#8217;s go!</th><th id='likert_col_2_89_4' scope='col' role='presentation' class='gsurvey-likert-choice-label'>Unsure or neutral to this</th><th id='likert_col_3_89_4' scope='col' role='presentation' class='gsurvey-likert-choice-label'>No way!</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td data-label='Great idea - let&#039;s go!' class='gsurvey-likert-choice'><input name='input_4' type='radio' value='glikertcol124cca797'  id='choice_89_4_1'    aria-labelledby='likert_col_1_89_4'/></td><td data-label='Unsure or neutral to this' class='gsurvey-likert-choice'><input name='input_4' type='radio' value='glikertcol4a379a1df'  id='choice_89_4_2'    aria-labelledby='likert_col_2_89_4'/></td><td data-label='No way!' class='gsurvey-likert-choice'><input name='input_4' type='radio' value='glikertcol1511abd92'  id='choice_89_4_3'    aria-labelledby='likert_col_3_89_4'/></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div id=\"field_89_7\" class=\"gfield gfield--type-survey gfield--input-type-likert gfield--width-full field_sublabel_below gfield--no-description field_description_below field_validation_below gfield_visibility_visible gsurvey-survey-field \"  data-field-class=\"gsurvey-survey-field\" ><label class='gfield_label gform-field-label' >If the ESC does NOT have a policy requiring vaccination in order to play squash, would you